# Netlify redirects file for SEO
# This file handles protocol and subdomain redirects

# Force HTTPS and non-www
http://www.half-half-man.com/* https://half-half-man.com/:splat 301!
http://half-half-man.com/* https://half-half-man.com/:splat 301!
https://www.half-half-man.com/* https://half-half-man.com/:splat 301!

# Remove trailing slashes (except for root)
/*/ /:splat 301!

# Handle case sensitivity
/Projects /projects 301!
/Blog /blog 301!
/Contact /contact 301!
/Tech-Stack /tech-stack 301!
/Faq /faq 301!
/Privacy-Policy /privacy-policy 301!

# Handle old tech-stack URLs (redirect to correct ones)
/tech-stack/security /tech-stack/cybersecurity-practices 301!
/tech-stack/backend /tech-stack/code-engineering 301!
/tech-stack/frontend /tech-stack/nocode-solutions 301!
/tech-stack/tools /tech-stack/optimization-maintenance 301!

